Invocation Name: meme wash
des:
According to the CDC, scrubbing your hands for 20 seconds is needed to get your hands properly cleaned. However, it is hard to keep track of those 20 seconds, plus I am not confident in singing "Happy Birthdays". So, why not do it with some memes!
